addr: Hammersmith Road. Kensington. LONDON W14 8UX GB
title: Weekend Classic
desc: FIDE rated players may play in the U2000 or U1800 if they are rated below those levels irrespective of ECF grade. Players without a FIDE rating may play in the U2000 or U1800 provided they have an ECF grade below 175 or 150 respectively.  A half point bye can be taken in rounds 1-4 provided it is requested before the end of the previous round.  All moves in 90 minutes plus a 30 second increment per move from move 1. Default time: 1 hour after the scheduled start time.
